// Converted Go version of the uploaded Python Telegram AI bot/admin system.
// Uses only the Go standard library.
//
// Main parity goals:
//   - HTTP health/admin/AI endpoints
//   - Supabase REST tables: user_prefs, text_cache, conversation_history,
//     scheduled_broadcasts, ai_api_keys, blocked_users, bot_settings, bot_locks
//   - Dynamic API keys with SHA-256 storage
//   - Hugging Face text + OCR calls, Gemini audio/image fallback hooks
//   - Telegram long polling, basic commands, OCR, AI reply/TTS hook, admin broadcast
//   - Phnom Penh local time display and schedule parsing
//
// Run:
//
//	go mod tidy
//	go run .
//
// Important environment variables:
//
//	TELEGRAM_BOT_TOKEN, ADMIN_IDS, ADMIN_WEB_PASSWORD, FLASK_SECRET_KEY or WEB_SECRET_KEY
//	SUPABASE_URL, SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY or SUPABASE_KEY
//	HF_TOKEN, HF_MODEL, HF_OCR_MODEL
//	GEMINI_API_KEY, GEMINI_MODEL
//	REDIS_URL (optional)
//	EDGE_TTS_BIN and FFMPEG_BIN (optional; for local text-to-voice)
